Jewellery ERP & Girvi Management Platform

Dashboard Module Specification v1.0

Module Code: MOD-DASHBOARD
Priority: Critical MVP
Version: 1.0
Frontend: Flutter + BLoC
Backend: NestJS
Dependencies: Authentication Module, Girvi Module, Customer Module, Interest Module, Vault Module, Compliance Module, Sales Module, Purchase Module, Savings Module, Reports Module

⸻

1. Module Purpose

The Dashboard Module serves as the operational command center of the Jewellery ERP platform.

It provides real-time visibility into business performance, operational status, financial health, compliance status, and pending actions.

The dashboard must allow owners, managers, and staff to immediately understand the current state of the business without navigating into individual modules.

