6. Core Business Rules

BR-DASH-001

Dashboard data refreshes automatically.

BR-DASH-002

Role permissions determine widget visibility.

BR-DASH-003

Dashboard must load within 3 seconds.

BR-DASH-004

All KPI values sourced from authoritative modules.

BR-DASH-005

Alerts must be prioritized.

BR-DASH-006

Dashboard supports offline cache.

BR-DASH-007

Financial metrics are read-only.

BR-DASH-008

Dashboard actions require permission validation.

